simple cellular automata.
can take some default pattern / rules (hardwired into the code) or read from rle files.
spread up into different cuncurrent processes ( requirement of the school project )

related article published here: http://ceur-ws.org/Vol-1107/paper6.pdf



HOW TO USE:

make all
./gestore

select the kind of evolution you want to see from the pop up menu

from the other terminal, select the kind of matrix initialization you like (R for manual - use space bar to "kill" cells - R for random with probability 1/3 )

to quit press Ctrl+C
